At the current moment (`konva@4.0.16`) that is not possible to do directly with `Konva` API. But you can make a workaround by placing a shape inside the rotated group.

```javascript
const group = new Konva.Group({
  x: stage.width() / 2,
  y: stage.height() / 2,
  rotation: 90
});
layer.add(group);

